data.description: UPDATE: SELLERS PAYING $5.000 TOWARD BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS. Beautiful and spacious 4 bedroom 3.5 bath home in a gated community. Short-term rentals permitted and just a short distance from the parks. Lots of restaurants  and shopping within a 5 minute drive. Community includes a playground and refreshing community pool. Low monthly HOA fee. Investors look no further, this is the perfect investment property. Ring bell & cameras do not convey. UPDATE: Sellers have decided that all appliances convey so stove, refrigerator, washer, & dryer will be part of the sale!
